<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="feature-v">feature <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fiːtʃə(r)/    美 /'fiːtʃər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>是...的特征；以...为特色</strong></h4>
<p>to include sb / sth as an important part：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This store features round-the-clock service.
这家商店的特色是24小时服务。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The film featured Allen Rickman as a professor.
这部电影由艾伦·里克曼饰演一位教授。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>起重要作用；占重要地位</strong></h4>
<p>to have an important part in sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Fish <strong>features in</strong> the Japanese diet.
鱼在日本人的饮食中占重要地位。</p></div></div>